        <h1>HeartBeat Library</h1>

        <div class="intro" style="font-weight: bold;">
        <p class="subtext">Update! I took some pictures of possible locations and so those are all below. I'm not like deadset on going to any of them but they could be cool to explore. I'm curious what you have in mind. Also the pictures suck because they're from my car mainly</p>
        <p class="subtext">I would love to get a range of close-ups and like setting shots of me inside this "world" that I'm trying to build, but I don't have any specific locations</p>
        </div>

        <div class="location">

            <div class="images">
                <img class="location-image" src="/content/images/HeartBeat_Ideation/locations/developments/IMG_1235.jpeg">
