            </div>
            <div class="caption">

                <p class="title" id="location-title">
                    My Old High School (Olentangy Orange High School)
                </p>
                <p class="description">
                    To be honest, I don't know what makes a good location for photos. But when I think of suburbia, I think high school and where I grew up. Also, when I think about visual symbolism for this EP, I think about things that make your heart beat fast, and things like soccer goals or tennis courts are derivative of that. It could be cool to include some of that.
                    <ul>
                        <p class="list-p">What I Like</p>
                            <li>- Suburbia vibes, personal connection</li>
                            <li>- Streetlamp lighting</li>
                            <li>- A couple of soccer goals and tennis courts but idk</li>
                        <p class="list-p">What I Don't Like</p>
                            <li>- No standout spot, just empty parking lots and vibes under streetlights</li>
                    </ul>
                </p>

