        <div class="intro" style="font-weight: bold;">
        <p class="subtext">Hey Ben! This is just a library for some inspiration regarding my own creative direction for the EP I'm working on. It's called HeartBeat and is about my relationship with music. As for where you come in, I'm open to any suggestions or ideas you have, but I mainly just need photos of myself to worldbuild and for EPK type stuff. Att the bottom, there are some photos of yours that I LOVE! Excited to see what comes out of this.</p>
        <p class="subtext">Depending on how deep you wanna get into it, there's visual influences, actual audio files of the songs, some stream-of-consciousness stuff, context, etc. But no pressure to read it all, I just would rather provide more information and inspiration than not enough. I also don't have any specific expectations out of it, though.</p>
        <p class="subtext">Briefly, some current inspirations in mind are heavy, deep colors, intimacy, medical devices, abstraction, noise, electronics, nighttime skies, that one Snapchat filter where you vomit rainbows, escapism and suburbia, extreme color, dead pixels, <input type="text" placeholder="you name it"></p>
        <p class="subtext">p.s. this webpage is not built the best</p>
        </div>
